name: Validate_isFalseTest
description: Unit tests for the Validate.isFalse method.

test_cases.name: testIsFalse_withFalseValue
test_cases.description: Tests that no exception is thrown when Validate.isFalse is called with a false value.

test_cases.name: testIsFalse_withTrueValue
test_cases.description: Tests that a ValidationException is thrown with the correct message when Validate.isFalse is called with a true value.
